thread.title: Kerim El Gabaili
thread.title_full: Servcorp reviewed by Kerim El Gabaili

author: Kerim El Gabaili
title: Kerim El Gabaili
text: Our decentralized business model is taking advantage of a sophisticated but yet simple platform that allows us to enjoy more personal time and increase work productive. Servcorp is an integral part of the puzzle that has allowed us to create this new business and life model. The level of professional staff at Servcorp is second to no office I have worked into, they represent us on the phone and in the office extremely professionally and we thank them for their support.
